{"tid":658452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WTO仲裁中國自居受害者 美方：愛麗絲夢遊仙境","createTime":"2018-05-09T04:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T19:00:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":215,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"7970d7674789f5b71e64971a8afca5db42d8a9f5","tid":658452,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美中貿易戰延燒進世貿組織WTO，中方認為美國故意阻礙仲裁，美方則回酸，「我們現在進入愛麗絲夢遊仙境的世界了，黑色是白色，向上就是向下」。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，中國認為，川普用鋼鋁稅與知識產權等方面壓迫中國，危害到WTO體系，此外，中國認為美方阻礙WTO仲裁小組成員遴選程序，中國常駐WTO代表張向晨呼籲恢復WTO上訴機構運作。<br />\n報導指出，對此，美方代表Dennis Shea認為WTO上訴機構缺乏信任，負責裁定者無視<br />\n規則，對WTO做出成員國無法接受的解讀，美方阻止部分裁決人選的任命。<br />\nDennis Shea還酸，中國是世上最大的自我保護型經濟，卻宣稱捍衛貿易自由，「我們現在進入愛麗絲夢遊仙境的世界了，黑色是白色，向上就是向下」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2419884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2419884&d=TSnP4WbJqntNZ1aUBGXHqjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=18f4ac9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2419884&h=66e4c4ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2419884</a>"},{"pid":"ea075c93a9842e8b9ce9faa472ebc2978b77a167","tid":658452,"uid":57376,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"口交部無稿唔識反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b91aa011958889eb99e68ec4cacb6ca2285654","tid":658452,"uid":58552,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:12:08.000Z","msg":"Facebook google WhatsApp 被禁<br />\nWe7 微博全球通用<br />\nWto講幾句"},{"pid":"f22d6db00e96f09bcd4b76666cb9292dec7ca518","tid":658452,"uid":55913,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"五毛快d嚟話連登仔炒車啦"},{"pid":"268c65620f77ddf8a42c86f01003783e8ecc41a7","tid":658452,"uid":61280,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:18:21.000Z